channel.description:
Minigames ranging from zombies to pest control we have it all. Anything you could want, we got it, and if we don't we'll do our best to add it. 317 loading 562, once we get to 15 players I will host a hide n seek. We have events such as pking "king of the hill" which the winner is rewarded a kills cape and other events all the time hosted by myself. Come and give us a shot!!
